title: 92.685 LAND MANAGEMENT ACCOUNT.
text: The land management account is created in the natural resources fund. Money credited to the account is appropriated annually to the commissioner of natural resources to administer the utility easement program under section 84.415, the easement program under section 84.63, the road easement program under section 84.631, the easement release program under section 84.632, and the trail easement program under section 85.015, subdivision 1b.
